# TrendyWheels Windsurf Rules

## Monorepo: pnpm workspaces + Turborepo at /opt/trendywheels
## Apps: api (Express+TS), mobile (Expo), admin/support/inventory (Next.js 14)
## Packages: @trendywheels/{db,types,api-client,validators,ui-tokens,ui-web,ui-mobile,i18n}

## TypeScript strict. No `any`. Use `import type`. Explicit return types.
## Security: no secrets in code, zod validation at boundaries, no PII in logs.
## Design: blue gradient #1E50B4→#3B82F6, neon green #00FF00, dark #0F172A. Use ui-tokens.
## Mobile: Reanimated 2, FlashList, expo-image, expo-secure-store, 44px touch targets.
## Web: Shadcn/ui, Tailwind, Recharts, Server Components, Lighthouse ≥90.
## API: layered (routes→controllers→services→repos), pino logs, JWT RS256, rate limit.
## Git: Conventional Commits with scope. PR required for main.
## Testing: ≥70% coverage global, ≥85% on auth/booking/payments.
